    "title": "Opening for Store Manager at McDonald's India Digital Technologies",
    "description": "Grow your career with McDonald's India Digital Technologies! We are hiring a Store Manager for our Lucknow team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout McDonald's India Digital Technologies:\nMcDonald's India Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n• Proficiency in Loss Prevention\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Lucknow, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with McDonald's India Digital Technologies!",
